{"code": 0, "data": [{"cid": 1318472, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 259357, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "很多人还是会跟你说 gpa 卷多了无用。\n", "timestamp": 1616503004, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1318480, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 259357, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "多少算绩点高高呀", "timestamp": 1616503079, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1318486, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 259357, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "tier1绩点高高的绝对王者当然无敌，校强我渣才是真的心痛", "timestamp": 1616503112, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1318493, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 259357, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Bob: 牛剑3.7是公开的底线，但不排除例外，如果大神特别强学校会放宽要求", "timestamp": 1616503214, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1318504, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 259357, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 保持清醒，如果要出国申请，当然有用（", "timestamp": 1616503275, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1318517, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 259357, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "dz您观察绩点大概在申请phd中能起多大作用呢", "timestamp": 1616503353, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1318519, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 259357, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "有学长说绩点不重要,科研是王者,现在就有点纠结绩点要不要再救一救", "timestamp": 1616503380, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1318531, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 259357, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Carol: 那取决于科研有多强，两个都要是最好的，如果科研很强，绩点可以稍微不那么重要。绩点不够的坏处在于，学校会预判你学习能力不足以通过博资考………", "timestamp": 1616503489, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1318538, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 259357, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "再高的GPA也没有paper有用，导师是要能做出成果的人，收做题家有什么用？当然，都没有高质量paper的情况下，换位想想，如果你是导师，那也只能比GPA了吧", "timestamp": 1616503553, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1318544, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 259357, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Carol: 关于这点dz收到过学校非常委婉的提醒………我们的博资考是非常困难的，请确保你有足够的能力通过考试，否则将无法继续…🌚 ", "timestamp": 1616503598, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1318551, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 259357, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 呜呜dz想申的方向比较难出paper,一般好像都是卷暑研推荐信这种qwq", "timestamp": 1616503659, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1318559, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 259357, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Dave: Dave预判了导师的预判，dz同意。只是补充一点，有的学校admission team有权否决faculty的提名，简言之就是因为绩点会被招办刷下去………但这取决于不同的学校，不是绝对真理", "timestamp": 1616503742, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1318572, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 259357, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 顶校一般不会发生这种事吧，除非是认为学生和老师之间发生了不正当交易", "timestamp": 1616503859, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1318584, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 259357, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Dave: （情况就是这么个情况，Dave真的很懂，dz没好明说这点😂 ）", "timestamp": 1616503946, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1318602, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 259357, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "这个洞本意是吐槽dz校强我渣的无奈，顺便羡慕外校绩点很高的申请人………🌚 申phd的重要性排序当然是paper 大于gpa，但是dz吃了gpa低的亏，还是劝学弟学妹们不要太放飞gpa🌚 ", "timestamp": 1616504086, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1318799, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 259357, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 导师能不能直接要人取决于强committee还是弱committee吧", "timestamp": 1616506220, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1318846, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Francis", "pid": 259357, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "感觉科研和connection 比较重要，有机会要出去交换，可以自己申请自费交换", "timestamp": 1616506982, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1318849, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Francis", "pid": 259357, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Francis: GPA也很重要5555 申请好难", "timestamp": 1616507006, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1320535, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Grace", "pid": 259357, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "所有都重要，只是个加权的权重分配问题。gpa的重要程度是conditional的，paper越多gpa越不重要，没paper就得要你gpa3.9了", "timestamp": 1616536526, "type": "text", "url": ""}], "post": {"deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "likenum": 8, "pid": 259357, "reply": 19, "tag": null, "text": "申请季观察有感，国内高校tier 2绩点高高的申请选手真的比tier 1绩点低低的申请选手吃香太多了………", "timestamp": 1616502899, "type": "text", "updated_at": 1616536524, "url": "", "vote": {}}}